    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用远程同乐功能在Steam上游玩</h2><br>与朋友一起踏上《UnPlugged》冒险之旅。与朋友在一个充满挑战的本地合作模式中合作，作为两名机器人共同解决困难的谜题和迷宫，展开一场史诗般的冒险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>保持电力供应充足</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/8a88eba738ce66e2c4d38b08a82d81d3.poster.avif?t=1732293570\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/8a88eba738ce66e2c4d38b08a82d81d3.webm?t=1732293570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>两个机器人都需要电源才能运作。保持连接到电源，或者准备一个备用电源，并确保你的朋友也有电源可以运作！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体验具有挑战性的游戏玩法</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/a4b1e0db05770d42e2abda0083a3b59c.poster.avif?t=1732293570\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/a4b1e0db05770d42e2abda0083a3b59c.webm?t=1732293570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你和你的同伴通过协同合作，利用各种附件和完美的配合，穿越谜题和危险的场景，最终到达目的地。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与朋友一起找到通往前方的道路</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/7893722f9b9f26ebfde0d7b8d5ddff98.poster.avif?t=1732293570\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142930/extras/7893722f9b9f26ebfde0d7b8d5ddff98.webm?t=1732293570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>使用团队合作来解决谜题、克服障碍，并为你和你的同伴找到电源。<br><br>在与朋友一起穿越科幻实验室的冒险中，考验你们的友谊。解锁并掌握新的附件。在保持连接电源并管理电力储备的同时，互相帮助摆脱危险的境地！<br><br>请注意：此产品仅支持合作模式。使用 Steam 的“远程同乐”功能，与朋友一起体验整个游戏。",
